            . I am <rs id="t18330103-52-viclabel309" type="occupation">master of the <placeName id="t18330103-52-crimeloc310">workhouse of St. Botolph, Aldgate</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t18330103-52-crimeloc310" type="placeName" value="workhouse of St. Botolph, Aldgate"></interp>
